  "response": "Not at all! It's perfectly normal for adults to enjoy watching cartoons. Many animated shows and films are created with complex themes and humor that can appeal to both children and adults. Additionally, nostalgia plays a significant role, as revisiting favorite cartoons from childhood can bring comfort and joy. There are also numerous cartoons specifically designed for adult audiences, such as \"Rick and Morty,\" \"BoJack Horseman,\" and \"Archer.\" Ultimately, enjoying cartoons is just another form of entertainment, and everyone has their own preferences and tastes.",
